Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.98,SIGN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs72\pos(360,357)}Open Seams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm L.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is L?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not quite the image I had of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Yagami, I'm with the police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ukita.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.03,0:00:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, the five of us..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.59,0:00:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you playing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I was Kira, you'd be dead by now, Yagami Souichirou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to kill, Kira needs a face and a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you should know this by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to carelessly reveal your names.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.72,0:00:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try to value our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that the face is essential, {\alpha&HFF&}but I've heard nothing about Kira needing to know the victim's name as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that the face is essential, but I've heard nothing about Kira needing to know the victim's name as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.40,0:01:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the high profile criminals whose real names are unknown or were reported wrongly have escaped Kira's wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an issue that's also been discussed at Investigative Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Standing around there chatting is all very well, but please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.. okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.37,0:01:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must ask you to switch off all cell phones, laptops and other transmission devices and leave them on the table there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L! {\alpha&HFF&}Are you trying to suggest that we'd use our cell phones to let people listen in on this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L! Are you trying to suggest that we'd use our cell phones to let people listen in on this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.93,0:01:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just forget about that now and do as he asks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've known from the start the he's the cautious type, but it's hard to tell if he really trusts us or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... {\alpha&HFF&}it's just that I can't stand people's phones going off while I'm trying to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.34,0:01:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... it's just that I can't stand people's phones going off while I'm trying to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better tell you this now.. {\alpha&HFF&}I don't want anyone making notes for anyone of what's being discussed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.51,0:01:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better tell you this now.. I don't want anyone making notes for anyone of what's being discussed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.92,0:01:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err... L?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, from now on, call me "Ryuuzaki" instead of "L", just to be on the safe side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.39,0:02:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case.. uh, Ryuuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you already know that Kira needs both a name and face, why don't we just withhold criminal information from the media? Surely that will reduce the number of victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we did that, members of the public would end up being killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Members of the public?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is immature, and is a bad loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Immature?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, because I'm also immature and hate to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuzaki, could you explain that better for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I used that TV broadcast to challenge Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}despite the fact that Kira had only killed criminals up until then, they killed the fake version of me without any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I used that TV broadcast to challenge Kira, despite the fact that Kira had only killed criminals up until then, {\alpha&HFF&}they killed the fake version of me without any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.04,0:03:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I used that TV broadcast to challenge Kira, despite the fact that Kira had only killed criminals up until then, they killed the fake version of me without any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I disclosed the fact that I knew they were from the Kanto region of Japan, {\alpha&HFF&}they immediately began to kill mainly Japanese criminals as if to say, "So what?".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I disclosed the fact that I knew they were from the Kanto region of Japan, they immediately began to kill mainly Japanese criminals as if to say, "So what?".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of backing down from my provocations, they have been aggressively returning them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you try to withhold information from someone who acts like this, what do you think will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are no proper criminals to kill, they'll go after the petty ones, if there there aren't any of them, they'll be targeting the innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.09,0:03:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone on this planet is being held hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm not the one who's in the wrong here. {\alpha&HFF&}Those who try to hide the criminals from me are the ones who are in the wrong."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm not the one who's in the wrong here. Those who try to hide the criminals from me are the ones who are in the wrong."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is how Kira thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything, we should really be thinking of ways of using the media to our own advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Americans are angered by the murders of their FBI agents. The entire world turns against Kira. Approximately 1,500 investigators from powerful nations enter Japan."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will have a lot more than the FBI to deal with this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll begin to perceive absolutely everyone to be their enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling trapped, Kira will give us some kind of reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll think that there are 1,500 people after them, even though in reality there's only seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And since the investigators don't exist, they can't kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could really work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, let me tell you some of my thoughts regarding this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira is a loner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, they were accessing information from the previous headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tell that they're a loner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a minute Aizawa. Let's listen to all of Ryuuzaki's reasonings first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to kill, they require both a name and a face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can also manipulate the time of death, and to some extent, the victim's movements prior to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having absorbed what I just said, {\alpha&HFF&}please listen closely to the following.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having absorbed what I just said, please listen closely to the following.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the 14th December, {\alpha&HFF&}twelve FBI agents entered Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the 14th December, twelve FBI agents entered Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.17,0:05:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the 19th December, {\alpha&HFF&}Kira is evidently using prisoners as test subjects in order to study how they could manipulate the victim's movements before death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the 19th December, Kira is evidently using prisoners as test subjects in order to study how they could manipulate the victim's movements before death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, {\alpha&HFF&}during these five days, Kira became aware of the FBI's presence in Japan, and felt threatened by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, during these five days, {\alpha&HFF&}Kira became aware of the FBI's presence in Japan, and felt threatened by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To put it simply, during these five days, Kira became aware of the FBI's presence in Japan, and felt threatened by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From this we can deduce that to kill the FBI agents whose names and faces they didn't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira found it necessary to experiment to see how far they could manipulate someone's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then on the 27th December...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:06:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was able to put files containing the names and faces of everyone involved into the hands of every agent on the team, {\alpha&HFF&}and succeeded in killing them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was able to put files containing the names and faces of everyone involved into the hands of every agent on the team, and succeeded in killing them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, it's almost impossible to tell whose files I looked at in order to kill the agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But.. {\alpha&HFF&}the fact that I encountered Ray Penber must never be discovered by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.46,0:06:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But.. the fact that I encountered Ray Penber must never be discovered by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Not using the Death Note today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for those "exams"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to still be trying to study for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The period from the 19th to the 27th December... {\alpha&HFF&}is when I've been most active.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The period from the 19th to the 27th December... is when I've been most active.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During this time, as far as we can tell, 23 people have died of a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These 23 people were all either suspected criminals or previous offenders, either guilty of lesser crimes or only suspected of wrongdoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is clearly different from Kira's previous targets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This suggests that for Kira to kill the FBI agents, {\alpha&HFF&}it was necessary to manipulate these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This suggests that for Kira to kill the FBI agents, it was necessary to manipulate these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They killed 23 people to make it harder for us to identify who was actually killed as part of the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.93,0:07:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, it's likely that Kira only used a few of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that there were eight days between the tests being performed, and Kira acting,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,indicates that they allowed the agents to investigate as many people as possible to draw suspicion away from themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Consequently, Kira must be someone that was under investigation by the FBI between the 14th and the 19th.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've compiled data from the FBI and other necessary information together, although, I'm afraid that I won't let you take them away from here--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we know this much, we should be able to make progress, even if it's just the seven of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to check up on the past movements of the FBI and the heart attack victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should split into two groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't a lot of people who had access to police information and were investigated during that period.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Ryuuzaki, {\alpha&HFF&}let me ask you one thing. You said that like Kira, you hate to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Ryuuzaki, let me ask you one thing. {\alpha&HFF&}You said that like Kira, you hate to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Ryuuzaki, let me ask you one thing. You said that like Kira, you hate to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't the fact that you've had to show us your face mean that you've lost to Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I've had to show my face and allowed twelve FBI agents to die, are my losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will win in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time that I've had to lay down my life in a contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As people willing to place our lives on the line, let's show Kira... {\alpha&HFF&}that justice will always prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As people willing to place our lives on the line, let's show Kira... that justice will always prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice will triumph!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's do this, Ryuuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.71,0:08:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first saw him, I wondered whether he was the real thing, {\alpha&HFF&}but now I'm sure that he's the real L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I first saw him, I wondered whether he was the real thing, but now I'm sure that he's the real L.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:09:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'd like to determine that Kira is not amongst us by having a one-on-one discussion with each of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He still doesn't trust us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.03,0:09:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reasonable request.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira really is getting information from the police, {\alpha&HFF&}there's a high possibility that he could be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira really is getting information from the police, there's a high possibility that he could be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! If they stayed on the case, they'd get to see Ryuuzaki's face, wouldn't they...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what it means to put your life on the line...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So far so good...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more... {\alpha&HFF&}if only there was one more conclusive fact..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more... if only there was one more conclusive fact..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was a hole in my plan... {\alpha&HFF&}if a single fact gets out... it could cost me my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was a hole in my plan... if a single fact gets out... {\alpha&HFF&}it could cost me my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was a hole in my plan... if a single fact gets out... it could cost me my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one thing...
Comment: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EYECATCHERS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finished studying then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, there were no holes in my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The riskiest incident was the bus hi-jacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way that they'll be able to connect that to Kira, {\alpha&HFF&}since L and the police believe that Kira can only kill via heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way that they'll be able to connect that to Kira, since L and the police believe that Kira can only kill via heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, if that fact was found out, it would become a massive hole in my plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad's working all night without a change of clothes, so we should take some over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I promised to go to the New Year's festival with my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.02,0:10:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be nice to have a change of scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky! Thank you, onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this means that you get to go spy on Police Headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I go, I'll only get as far as the reception desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking a page with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to kill someone in the open?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made a habit of doing this every time I go out... just in case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day... {\alpha&HFF&}I remember Ray saying he was going to Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day... I remember Ray saying he was going to Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that same day, four relatively innocent people died of heart attacks around Shinjuku station...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that bus hi-jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can kill people by means other than just a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:44.28,Background,,0000,0000,0000,,The number you have dialled is unavailable..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.73,0:11:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's an important meeting going on or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, {\alpha&HFF&}please let me speak to the Investigative Headquarters in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, please let me speak to the Investigative Headquarters in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:12:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like we keep saying, there's no one there at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one at headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His cell phone redirects to the answering machine too. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a way in which I can contact them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is extremely important; it's about the Kira investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kira investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.43,0:12:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll try ringing headquarters again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Chief Yagami Souichirou's son, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought him a change of clothes, but seeing that he doesn't seem to be around, could you look after them for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Light-kun, good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err.. I'm sorry I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was also here that time your advice helped us in solving that insurance money killing case, last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is that it? Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I write my name here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been trying to rationalize the Kira investigation too, Light-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. If all goes well, I'll solve it before L does.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Solve it before L?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but it really does seem like there's nobody at headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, try to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass on your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good. I've got to speak to them directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.71,0:13:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. {\alpha&HFF&}My father's the Chief Investigator for the Kira investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. My father's the Chief Investigator for the Kira investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like, I could try to get a hold of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to do that immediately though, his cell phone is switched off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the deaths of the FBI agents, a lot of people have been resigning within headquarters because they fear Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can imagine it being a very hectic time for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Light-kun, you shouldn't tell members of the public things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are already gossiping about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, this person can be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it in her eyes. She's an intelligent and prudent person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of what happened to the FBI, {\alpha&HFF&}you've realized that there's a problem within the police force, and that's why you wish to speak directly to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.54,0:13:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of what happened to the FBI, you've realized that there's a problem within the police force, {\alpha&HFF&}and that's why you wish to speak directly to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of what happened to the FBI, you've realized that there's a problem within the police force, and that's why you wish to speak directly to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figure that my father will eventually pick up his voice-mail and call me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind waiting, you can speak to him directly then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Of course, I can't give you my father's number, but you're welcome to use my cell phone to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it won't mean much until you decide to trust me or my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the sudden cheerful demeanor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you've fooled her, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've certainly got a lot of courage to try and get involved with the Kira investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to your thinking, Kira... {\alpha&HFF&}um, could I at least ask you for your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to your thinking, Kira... um, {\alpha&HFF&}could I at least ask you for your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to your thinking, Kira... um, could I at least ask you for your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yagami Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's written as "god of the night" (夜神), and then the character for "moon" (月), except you read it as "light".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unusual, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Maki Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spelt with the characters "interval" (間) and "tree" (木), and then "illuminate" (照) and "child" (子).
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's Maki-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maki-san, {\alpha&HFF&}according to my theory, Kira can manipulate people before killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maki-san, according to my theory, {\alpha&HFF&}Kira can manipulate people before killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maki-san, according to my theory, Kira can manipulate people before killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking the exact same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kira can manipulate people before killing them", but that's not all. If I'm right... {\alpha&HFF&}Kira can kill people using methods other than heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Kira can manipulate people before killing them", but that's not all. If I'm right... Kira can kill people using methods other than heart attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone else has realized yet, {\alpha&HFF&}but if we assume this to be true... I think Kira knows they'll be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone else has realized yet, but if we assume this to be true... {\alpha&HFF&}I think Kira knows they'll be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone else has realized yet, but if we assume this to be true... I think Kira knows they'll be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't thought that far ahead yet, {\alpha&HFF&}but if that's true, the murders that Kira really wants to hide... will be by methods other than heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't thought that far ahead yet, but if that's true, the murders that Kira really wants to hide... will be by methods other than heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}and I think someone I know met Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.61,0:15:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and I think someone I know met Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.67,0:15:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.. {\alpha&HFF&}it's true that if you told the police that, they'd never believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.04,0:16:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.. it's true that if you told the police that, they'd never believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}that's why I wanted to speak to someone in the investigation directly, and explain that I've got a reasonable case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's why I wanted to speak to someone in the investigation directly, and explain that I've got a reasonable case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in that case, wouldn't it be better if the person who met Kira talked to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person is no longer with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was one of the FBI agents who came to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An FBI investigator... {\alpha&HFF&}who met Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An FBI investigator... who met Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was also my fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he was randomly caught up in a bus hi-jacking, {\alpha&HFF&}but if my theory is correct, he met Kira on that bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he was randomly caught up in a bus hi-jacking, but if my theory is correct, he met Kira on that bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ray... {\alpha&HFF&}Penber!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ray... Penber!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.. I had no idea that you'd lost your fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, {\alpha&HFF&}why do you think he met Kira on that bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why do you think he met Kira on that bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After being caught up in that bus hi-jacking, {\alpha&HFF&}he died eight days later along with eleven other FBI agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After being caught up in that bus hi-jacking, he died eight days later along with eleven other FBI agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two days earlier, the culprit of the bus hi-jacking committed a bank robbery, {\alpha&HFF&}and in the end he died in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two days earlier, the culprit of the bus hi-jacking committed a bank robbery, and in the end he died in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something that has been seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only imagine that the bus hi-jack was set up, so that Kira could obtain information on the FBI agents in Japan that they intended to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the culprit ended up dead in an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, heart attacks are not the only way that Kira can kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bus hi-jack culprit didn't die of a heart attack. {\alpha&HFF&}Therefore, Kira must be able to kill via methods other than heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bus hi-jack culprit didn't die of a heart attack. Therefore, Kira must be able to kill via methods other than heart attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think your story requires a few leaps in logic...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:18:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the only explanation is that the culprit was being manipulated by Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.67,0:18:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since he told me about the bus hi-jacking, something has been on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, I asked him about it when he was in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he didn't give me a name, he very clearly said...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That he had no choice but to show someone on the bus his FBI ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The investigation was kept secret from the Japanese police, {\alpha&HFF&}so there were orders that they were to never show their ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The investigation was kept secret from the Japanese police, so there were orders that they were to never show their ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the fact that FBI agents were in Japan must have come from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the "hole" that Light has been worrying about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. {\alpha&HFF&}A truth that only you could know, and vengeance for the fiancé that was taken from you, have led you to this answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. A truth that only you could know, and vengeance for the fiancé that was taken from you, have led you to this answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kira can kill people through other methods than just a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:18:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have incredible powers of deduction, yet you are blinded by personal feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like this is very much aggressive intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, {\alpha&HFF&}there are ample reasons to justify investigating this theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there are ample reasons to justify investigating this theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your testimony will be very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're right, it'll be like you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will soon be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, {\alpha&HFF&}the person who your fiancé showed his ID to in the bus... is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the person who your fiancé showed his ID to in the bus... {\alpha&HFF&}is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the person who your fiancé showed his ID to in the bus... is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this woman had got to the police before I got to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems that gods other than the Shinigami... {\alpha&HFF&}are on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it seems that gods other than the Shinigami... are on my side.
